   "source": [
    "## Sensitivity analysis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "b409c0cb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Imports\n",
    "from gfeatpy.observation import Range\n",
    "from gfeatpy import planet\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "b8c60917",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Default values\n",
    "Nr = 295\n",
    "Nd = 19\n",
    "I = np.deg2rad(88)\n",
    "rho = 400e3\n",
    "l_max = 100"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "7be47108",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Define error spectra\n",
    "mwi = lambda f: 2.62 * np.sqrt(1 + (0.003/f)**2) * 1e-6\n",
    "acc = lambda f: 1e-10 * np.sqrt(1 + (f/0.5)**4 + (0.005/f))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "bbeb1f76",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Semi-major axis sensitivity\n",
    "labels = []\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "\n",
    "l = np.arange(0, l_max+1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "for Nri in [316, 309, 302, 295, 289]:\n",
    "    range = Range(l_max, Nri, Nd, I, rho)\n",
    "    range.set_observation_error(mwi, acc)\n",
    "    range.solve()\n",
    "    labels.append(f\"h = {int((range.get_radius()  - planet.ae)/1000)} km\")\n",
    "    ax.semilogy(l[2:], range.rms_per_coefficient_per_degree()[2:])\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.legend(labels)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "bee2f41f",
   "metadata": {
    "nbsphinx-thumbnail": {
     "tooltip": "This tooltip message was defined in cell metadata"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Nominal inter-satellite separation sensitivity\n",
    "labels = []\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "\n",
    "l = np.arange(0, l_max+1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "for rho_i in np.arange(200e3, 1200e3, 200e3):\n",
    "    range = Range(l_max, Nr, Nd, I, rho_i)\n",
    "    range.set_observation_error(mwi, acc)\n",
    "    range.solve()\n",
    "    labels.append(f\"$\\\\rho_0$ = {int(rho_i/1e3)} km\")\n",
    "    ax.semilogy(l[2:], range.rms_per_coefficient_per_degree()[2:])\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.legend(labels)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "5d3a23d7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Inclination sensitivity\n",
    "labels = []\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "\n",
    "l = np.arange(0, l_max+1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "for I_i in np.deg2rad(np.arange(80, 92, 2)[::-1]):\n",
    "    range = Range(l_max, Nr, Nd, I_i, rho)\n",
    "    range.set_observation_error(mwi, acc)\n",
    "    range.solve()\n",
    "    labels.append(f\"$i$ = {int(np.rad2deg(I_i))}\")\n",
    "    ax.semilogy(l[2:], range.rms_per_coefficient_per_degree()[2:])\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.legend(labels)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  }
 ],
